snippet.title: Robo Legend Main Trailer
snippet.description: Robo Legend is a twin-stick shooter, action RPG where you take on hordes of robots, minigames, and missions to either save, or conquer, Gear Town.  Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1992480
